query:
INSERT INTO task_history (id, task_id, event_type, old_value, new_value, metadata)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
               RETURNING 
                   id as "id!: Uuid",
                   task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                   event_type as "event_type!: TaskHistoryEventType",
                   old_value,
                   new_value,
                   metadata,
                   created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
